# GG Krishi — MVP Quotation

**Digital MRV Infrastructure for Biochar Carbon Credit Verification**

---

| | |
|---|---|
| **Client** | GG Krishi Tech |
| **Project** | WhatsApp-Based Biochar Verification MVP |
| **Date** | 25 February 2026 |
| **Quote** | **₹1,00,000 INR** |

---

## What Was Delivered

A production-ready, end-to-end digital MRV (Monitoring, Reporting, Verification) system — from farmer WhatsApp scan to admin dashboard — built and deployed in a single session.

### 1. WhatsApp Verification Bot
- Full state-machine chatbot on WhatsApp Business Cloud API
- Automated 3-step flow: **QR Scan → GPS → Photo → Result**
- Handles edge cases: duplicate claims, wrong message types, re-scan rejection
- Real-time farmer notifications with status updates

### 2. AI-Powered Image Analysis
- **Gemini 2.0 Flash Vision** integration for field photo verification
- Detects: biochar presence, soil visibility, outdoor environment, screen capture fraud
- Returns structured confidence scores for every submission

### 3. Fraud Prevention Engine
- SHA-256 image hashing to prevent photo reuse across claims
- Weighted composite fraud scoring (AI confidence + duplicate detection)
- Automatic VERIFIED / REJECTED / PENDING decisions
- Impossible to claim the same bag twice

### 4. Admin Dashboard (Next.js)
- **Bags Page** — live bag inventory with status badges, QR code modal (always visible, status overlay)
- **History Page** — verification data table with filters, search, AI confidence bars, fraud score bars, GPS map links
- **Logs Page** — activity log viewer with level filters, expandable JSON details
- Auto-refreshing every 5 seconds for real-time monitoring

### 5. Cloud Database (Neon PostgreSQL)
- Production-grade hosted database (not local SQLite)
- 3 tables: Bags, Verifications, ActivityLogs
- Accessible from anywhere — ready for deployment

### 6. Comprehensive Backend Logging
- 15 typed event categories (BAG_CREATED, BAG_CLAIMED, VERIFICATION_REJECTED, etc.)
- Auto-detected log levels (INFO / WARN / ERROR)
- Full audit trail for every action in the system

